# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# .gitignore — slim public repo for the Colour Experience form.
#
# This repo only contains the files needed to DEPLOY the live form:
#   - docs/index.html         (served by GitHub Pages)
#   - apps_script_backend.gs  (backend code reference)
#   - README.md
#   - .gitignore
#
# Everything else (simulation pipeline, autocompiler, Flask server,
# other-platform deploy configs, study documents, etc.) lives only on
# the researcher's local disk and is never pushed.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Local development files (not for public) ──────────────────────────
file_shs_review/
color_check/
gith/
local_form_server.py
serve_public.py
google_form_submitter.py
sync_docs.py
generate_pdf_guide.py
generate_simulation_guide.py

# ── Other-platform deploy configs (kept local in case we migrate) ──────
Dockerfile
Procfile
requirements.txt
requirements-server.txt
runtime.txt
fly.toml
render.yaml

# ── Internal / setup docs (not for public) ────────────────────────────
DEPLOY.md
CLOUD_DEPLOY.md
GITHUB_PAGES_DEPLOY.md

# ── Runtime / build artefacts ──────────────────────────────────────────
local_responses.csv
local_submit_log.json
submitted_participants.json
*.pdf
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
.venv/
venv/

# ── OS / editor noise ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
.claude/
*.swp

# ── Excel and data files ───────────────────────────────────────────────
*.xlsx
*.xlsm
